# This program accepts all inputs of the form ba*b (b followed by any number of a's followed by b)
# This could easily be written using Transition mode, however, this program is meant to demonstrate how an acceptor would work using Manual mode
# This machine assumes the input alphabet consists of only a's and b's

IF a {
    REJECT
}

R
WHILE a {
    R
}

IF # {
    REJECT
}

R
IF # {
    ACCEPT
} ELSE {
    REJECT
}